-texas-uvalde-school-shooting-85074844","shortLocator":"https://web.archive.org/web/20260225233007/https://abcn.ws/3wWKt9M","section":"WNT","headline":"Biden in Texas following Uvalde school shooting","leadInText":"President Joe Biden attended a Mass at a Catholic Church in Uvalde, Texas, on Sunday afternoon. He said he met with victims and their families for three hours and their “pain is palpable.” ","issued":"2022-05-31T01:26:36Z","modified":"2025-01-20T15:44:27Z","contents":{"image":{"credit":"ABCNews.com","crops":[{"name":"raw","ratio":"16x9","url":"https://web.archive.org/web/20260225233007/https://edge.qa.s.aws.seabcnews.go.com/images/WNT/220530_wn_moore_hpMain_16x9_992.jpg"},{"name":"12x5","ratio":"12x5","url":"https://web.archive.org/web/20260225233007/https://edge.qa.s.aws.seabcnews.go.com/images/WNT/220530_wn_moore_hpMain_12x5_992.jpg"},{"name":"16x9","ratio":"16x9","url":"https://web.archive.org/web/20260225233007/https://edge.qa.s.aws.seabcnews.go.com/images/WNT/220530_wn_moore_hpMain_16x9_992.jpg"},{"name":"1x1","ratio":"1x1","url":"https://web.archive.org/web/20260225233007/https://edge.qa.s.aws.seabcnews.go.com/images/WNT/220530_wn_moore_hpMain_1x1_992.jpg"},{"name":"4x3","ratio":"4x3","url":"https://web.archive.org/web/20260225233007/https://edge.qa.s.aws.seabcnews.go.com/images/WNT/220530_wn_moore_hpMain_4x3_992.jpg"},{"name":"4x5","ratio":"4x5","url":"https://web.archive.org/web/20260225233007/https://edge.qa.s.aws.seabcnews.go.com/images/WNT/220530_wn_moore_hpMain_4x5_992.jpg"}],"description":"VIDEO: Biden in Texas following Uvalde school shooting"}},"duration":293000,"isLive":false}},{"id":"abcnews-video-85074809","type":"card","data":{"id":"85074809","type":"video","locator":"https://web.archive.org/web/20260225233007/https://abcnews.go.com/WNT/video/battle-continues-eastern-ukraine-french-journalist-killed-85074809","shortLocator":"https://web.archive.org/web/20260225233007/https://abcn.ws/3a8Cmzh","section":"WNT","headline":"Battle continues 